title: #131: The Grand Plan with Eddie Bravo
description: Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  This episode we welcome the man, the myth, the legend Eddie Bravo back to the show to discuss the chaotic world we live in. Thank you for your support.
